        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35378229/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35378229/" class="">第221页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jayway25/" class=" " title="Redoct">Redoct</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35378229">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">如果你读到这封信的时候，我的妈妈肯定在这里
